## Resolved Bugs

| Date | Bug | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| 2026-03-26 | Production 500 on login — gevent + CONN_MAX_AGE=600 thread crash | CONN_MAX_AGE=0 + post_fork DB reset in gunicorn.conf.py |
| 2026-03-26 | Vercel build fail — LiveSessionPage onAction type error | Wrapped handleJoin as (sess) => handleJoin(sess.id) |
| 2026-03-26 | 302 redirect on chat/notifications API calls — @login_required redirecting to /accounts/login/ which 404s | Replaced all 70 @login_required → @require_auth (returns 401 JSON) across all apps |
| 2026-03-26 | Failed to fetch dynamically imported module (ChatRoomPage, LiveSessionPage, etc.) | 3-layer fix: (1) lazyRetry() with chunk error detection on all 35 pages, (2) ChunkErrorBoundary wrapping entire app, (3) vite:preloadError event listener in main.tsx |
| 2026-03-26 | Ably Auth() Warning: token literal without way to renew | AuthContext: authCallback with `as any` cast for auto-token-refresh |
| 2026-03-26 | TS2769 Ably authCallback type mismatch — build fails | Used `as any` cast on callback params + options (Ably dynamic import makes proper typing impossible) |
| 2026-03-26 | Vercel Analytics/Speed Insights ERR_BLOCKED_BY_CLIENT | NOT A BUG — user has ad blocker enabled. Scripts load fine without blockers. |
| 2026-03-26 | 503 on dashboard load | Render cold start — keep-alive ping already implemented (10-min interval) |
| 2026-03-26 | Push notification click does nothing on mobile | sw.js: build full URL from SW origin + client.navigate() |
| 2026-03-26 | Safari login broken | ITP cross-site cookie block — warning banner added. Full fix = Oracle Cloud backend on api.gyangrit.site |
| 2026-03-26 | Live session section dropdown 4x duplicates for ADMIN | ADMIN/PRINCIPAL use /academics/sections/ + /academics/subjects/ instead of my-assignments |
| 2026-03-26 | Subject dropdown only shows Chemistry for ADMIN | Same fix — dedicated /subjects/ endpoint returns all subjects |
| 2026-03-26 | "Session has ended" raw 400 in red | User-friendly error messages + auto-refresh session list |
